four cisplatin-containing doublet commbinations in stage IVB recurrent or persistent cervical carcinoma: A Gynecologic Group Study. $J Clin Oncol. 2009;27(28):4649-4655.$', null, '<p><strong>Paclitaxel:</strong> 135 mg/m2 IV over 24 hours on day 1.</p><p><strong>Cisplatin:</strong> 75 mg/m2 IV on day 2<br>Repeat every 21 days for 6 cycles</p>', null);
